The room seems rather nice, with accommodations being laid out for you. However, it seems like there isn't a bathroom, so you'll need to go to the actual resort to do that. First things first, the bed. It's a twin sized bed, enough to fit one person unless they're really big. There are spare sheets still in their packaging under the bed, and 2 pillows are on the bed itself. This is where you'll probably be sleeping for most of your nights. Beside the bed is a nightstand with a lamp on it. Next, there's a desk opposite the bed in the room. The desk is supplied with basic office goods, like paper and pens. You'll be able to write whatever you want here, and work on whatever you want. There's a trash can beside the desk as well. A desk lamp sits on top. Finally, the wardrobe. This contains whatever your OC is wearing in their image in #〖👤〗character-info. However, there is another curious item in here. A large and puffy jacket, fitted to your OC is in the wardrobe. It's gray, with no logos or designs on it. It seems you're to wear this whenever you head outside. One last thing. On the desk of the room sits a little badge for your jacket. It's a badge of Monokuma's face on it. It's up to you if you want to put it on your jacket or not.
